Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12月的平均气温为23度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以游泳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次旅游会很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会允许那个人做独家采访呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后和自卫队的联合作战任务会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的秘密武器迟早也会曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再者，口头上的敷衍还是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！能来这个南方小岛我很高兴，不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于实地的采访…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会派一位很可爱的人做你的向导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太期待了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇，那就是人类的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对MU作战的最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根来彼方岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一个抽象艺术品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是从奈里亚神殿遗迹中运回来的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你违反了守密原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里都是相关人员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心？我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许如月博士知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人好像什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不清楚它的构造是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然她不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑道和机库均已清理至4级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有硬件方面的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与无人战机的协作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和地球联合使用的程序\N我们差不多都可以适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的问题在于维护保养部门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他们不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的技术的确不错，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人战机没有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂啊命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生在20世纪的人就喜欢那样虚幻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白人的坏毛病就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只相信能看见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:04:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我在客厅里放些黄色的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们两年来的第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你们都一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？真是有两年没见了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你邀我来这个小队，bunga mawar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.45,*note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}bunga mawar：印尼语，蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾尔菲·哈迪亚特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始，被任命为TERRA空军Alpha小队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了，祝你好运，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔菲·哈迪亚特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，是那个唯一从Overlord行动中\N生还的飞行员吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运女神？不，或者是死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tokyo Jupiter里面怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京塔真的是蓝的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间的话我一定要听听你的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过管理部了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让你到任后就去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威风凛凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打赌她是个“女神”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把现场的事情都扔给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的，从本州带来的纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，多谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有，我想让你给别人当一回向导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向导？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此，他就是那个“可爱的人”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天户通讯的贰神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们允许我对TERRA进行采访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么带他在人工岛转转就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了，如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！五味君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是从本州带的纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没变啊，亘理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有轻微的震动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来他挺合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自离开了故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个为拯救世界而战的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讽刺的语气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你误会了，我真是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把衣服放在那里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七森小姐，你和遥关系很好，是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，但我们还算不上挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥喜欢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她喜欢喝酒，我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为圣诞节准备吗？\N不问小惠的爱好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她比较容易了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和东京的差别并没有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家人分开后，不孤单吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真觉得痛苦，也没必要强忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊，你今天要调到战术部去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在分析部门进行实验时很合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经适应了岛上的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的，他很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他是不是遇上了好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？这是八云君的经验么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总一，那个记者怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个，处理了一些事情后就立刻去采访了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去本岛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到根来岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要留在这里一阵子\N他说要去找一个以后可以常去的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人到这里来干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是联合军的监察官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来监视你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们半夜一起偷跑出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你来找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些人中间你不感觉内心空虚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这种冷漠无情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是冷漠无情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我拿一瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个，那样是喝不到的，因为有个小球堵着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得把它转到凹槽里面去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在度假吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单身赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工薪族很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这个你能明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以多少我还能理解一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？那个…我开车，之后把比萨饼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送比萨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还有这种活啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“D-1出现，马上返回”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要工作了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，再会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个空瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话，退给商店可以拿到退瓶费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太平洋上确认的D-1全高为6000米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正以40公里的时速向根来彼方岛前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计作战时间为1408
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1408是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，那个\N那个是指14点08分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据现在大约20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标D-1很可能为两足步行型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据推测腿和生长出来的部分长度约为5千米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右两边的形状应该是完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？为什么只有腿说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能看到腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是这房子的主人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以打扰你一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从11点到13点方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离10000
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-1影像确认，在12点方向，情况确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机维持队形接近目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon在后方待机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解！了解！了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为我同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击中了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是站着的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是飘浮着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被外形误导了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha和Bravo，在16点方向散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blue队形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风水不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人住？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名牌上有三个不同的姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亲戚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个侄女和一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能依靠孩子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国小学生绘画比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2009年的参加者名单里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有神名绫人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候他五年级…\N如果现在还活着的话就有29岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我这里的绫人只有17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说，另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-1咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！让Alpha-1队撤回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha-1队没有回音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon正在放出量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在歌唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧，艾尔菲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我，注意敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心，只要他在座舱里就不会被电击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon活动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机师的生命维持降低至3级！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君，请回答！绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君！绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君！听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快，不做点什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开！滚开！滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开！滚开！滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tokyo…Jupiter？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响亮的音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在于战争之火中…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一局如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会我会再来拜访的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六道博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单机突入不明云层！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主张是违反军纪的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种战斗方式是会让你送命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你！你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要单机突入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为指挥官，我按最佳方式进行了判断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你是违反了军纪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁闭两天，就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何，监察官先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得我们很无耻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一个被绑架来的孩子为我们作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想，这次该轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后还请照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不能上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一直在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的风，不知不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹吹风，可以使人心情舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为家境问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京在哪个方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感觉它们之间有某种联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耸立的纯白冰树
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱着黑暗心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RahXephon第八乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰封圣诞夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界饱含着声音
